settings.title: Shipping Details
settings.text:
Want to know when your order will arrive and how much shipping will be? The shipping service, duration, and fees may differ depending on your delivery country. Here you will find a comprehensive overview.

Our minimum order value is €10.00 and dispatch takes place on working days, Monday to Friday.

The maximum weight for shipments outside Germany is 9kg - this corresponds to 6-7 pairs of sneakers.

Is your country not listed? Then it is possible that we do not deliver to you at the moment. You can find more information about current limitations regarding our delivery areas.

Search for your country to see all available shipping details.

Please note: Deliveries to third countries are tax-free export deliveries in accordance with Section 6 No. 1 of the German Value Added Tax Act (UStG).
If the delivery is made to third countries (non-EU), further customs duties, taxes or fees may have to be paid by the customer, but not to the Overkill (supplier), but to the customs or tax authorities responsible in your location. For more details, please ask the customs or tax authorities for details before ordering.
